# Day 1 — Introduction to Agents & Vibe Coding

Day 1 lays the foundation for the entire course by introducing the core concepts behind modern AI-native software development. Before building production-grade AI agents, it's important to understand the mindset shift happening across the software industry.

This module focuses on how software development is evolving from writing code manually to expressing intent and allowing intelligent systems to handle implementation. You'll learn the key mental models that power modern AI agents, how Vibe Coding differs from Agentic Engineering, and why Context Engineering is becoming one of the most valuable skills for developers.

